{
  "stem": "4361.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one of the Frenchmen suggested, why don't we go in the village and see if we can find some home because the Germans and the Nazis who lived there absconded?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It turned out when we were seeing all those Nazi personnel running, their heads, you know, in-- hidden, and we were looking down, they were running to the American-- to the Americans to be-- and-- and they surrendering to the Americans because they didn't want to be caught by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They knew what-- what would have happened to them with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's why they were running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- How was it for you to hear what was going on the camps?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How were you hearing it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And how is that affecting you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it affects me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It affects me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- I'm very-- I am very torn about it because raping occurs with every army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans raped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Nazis raped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't have to-- to go into more detail, but it-- and the Russians raped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is no question about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet, they liberated me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see the conflict?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yet, they liberated me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They liberated me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I also know, for instance, that not because they were Jew-lovers, not because Stalin was a great friend of the Jews, but certain things happened that so many Russian Jews were saved, Russian Jews who were not living under Nazi occupation.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm talking about the part of Russia that was not saved-- I mean, that was not occupied.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when-- when the Nazis began to push into Russia after [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Barbarosa, ?] after they declared war, Stalin give a command to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He withdrew his people and put them into-- around the Urals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were many Jews who were thus saved.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
